Subject: pinctrl: pinctrl-imx7ulp: add gpio_set_direction support
Git-commit: 26d1f4382225dfdcafd5d63d06531a90cba47c0f
Patch-mainline: v4.14-rc1
References: FATE#326248

Add gpio_set_direction support. This makes the driver support
GPIO input/output dynamically change from userspace.

